       | T(n - a) + 1, n > a 

T(n) = T(n - a) + 1 = (T(n - 2*a) + 1)+1 =
     = ((T(n - 3*a) + 1) + 1) + 1 =...=
     = T(n - k*a) + k ==
     | n-k*a =< a тому n/a-1=<k тому k := n/a-1 | 
     == n/a
     
