T(n) = | 1,             n = 0
       | T(n - 1) + 2**n, n >= 1

T(n) = T(n - 1) + 2**n =
     = (T(n - 2) + 2**(n-1)) + 2**n =
     = T(n - 3) + 2**(n-2) + 2**(n-1)+2**(n) =
     = ... = 1+2**1+2**2+...+2**n =
     = 1 + (2**(n+1)-2)=2**(n+1)-1

